    <summary>
		Monitors TeamCity builds and uses that to control a Delcom USB LED light
    </summary>
    <description>
Beacon is a little command-line tool that lets you connect a [Delcom USB RGB LED light](http://www.delcomproducts.com/products_usblmp.asp) to a set of [TeamCity](https://www.jetbrains.com/teamcity/) builds and use that to get an irrefutable indication on whether those builds succeeded, failed or are under investigation.

To get started just run the following command-line:

	beacon --url=http://yourteamcity.com --username=username --password=password --builds=build_id_1 build_id_2 etc

    </description> 
